description: Grab your broomstick and witches hat (but don't let it cover your eyes!) and join me, MauLer, Reaper, Baggage Claim, Nerdrotic and BlueCollarLoser at the Open Bar as we review Smile 2, give our thoughts on Blade being cancelled and the PR nightmare of Wicked.
title: Open Bar #116 - Wicked Disaster, Blade Cancelled, Smile 2 Review
